These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Color: lavender, yellow, emerald, fuchsia
Pet: ferret, fish, horse, lizard
1. Color:emerald is between Pet:horse and Pet:fish##2
2. Color:fuchsia is on the left or right of Pet:horse##3
3. Pet:horse is not to the left of Pet:horse##8
4. Pet:fish != Color:emerald##6
5. Color:emerald is somewhere to the right of Color:lavender##5
6. Color:lavender is on the right of Pet:ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | fuchsia  | lavender | emerald | yellow  |
| Pet   | ferret | horse   | lizard  | fish |

