.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Birthday: march, february, april, june
House: tower, farmhouse, wooden, modern
1. House:modern is not to the left of House:modern##8
2. Birthday:march is somewhere to the right of Birthday:june##5
3. Birthday:march == House:farmhouse##1
4. Birthday:june is between Birthday:march and Birthday:february##2
5. Birthday:february is somewhere between Birthday:april and House:tower##7
6. House:wooden is somewhere to the left of Birthday:february##5
7. House:tower is not to the left of House:tower##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | april | february          | june | march     |
| House    | wooden      | modern | tower | farmhouse |

